  'Weather Alert: Sandstorm', 'Monitor livestock closely', NULL, 'عاصفة رملية',
  'Dust storm warning issued. Move livestock to enclosed shelters to protect them from respiratory stress and eye irritation. Provide dust-free water and feed', 'تحذير من عاصفة رملية
